data.meta_description: DIALOGO 6 HAPPY BIRTHDAY - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Philip is 20 years old and will turn 21 on August 5th. For his birthday, Katherine is taking him out to a restaurant. They will likely order a birthday cake and the waiters will sing "Happy Birthday," which Philip thinks is embarrassing. Amy's birthday is September 17th. For her birthday that year, Philip plans to have a party and invites Amy and Katherine to come.
